{"tid":662981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎有刀客殺人並刺傷4人後被擊斃 伊斯蘭國承認責任","createTime":"2018-05-13T01:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T02:09:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bf779074d295e7332b096aee0a4ce4860364a3","tid":662981,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:36:15.000Z","msg":"法國巴黎發生持刀襲擊案，一名男子在市中心用刀殺死一人，刺傷另外4人，警員到場後，將他擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n警方仍在調查疑兇身分及動機。極端組織「伊斯蘭國」聲稱，疑兇是組織的「士兵」，他響應號召以美國在伊拉克及敘利亞的軍事盟友為目標。<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍說，法國再次付出「血的代價」，但強調向自由宣戰的人，法國不會向他們退讓。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長科隆慰問受害人及家屬，感謝警方迅速制伏疑犯。巴黎市長伊達爾戈表示，這個城市已經滿身傷痕，又對受害人說，巴黎所有人都會支持他們。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%9C%89%E5%88%80%E5%AE%A2%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%A6%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B74%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83-%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-232357432.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E5%2588%25BA%25E5%2582%25B74%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%2583-%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%2596%25AF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2589%25BF%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB-232357432.html&d=D3NCg31tFAP3E2nHj9EEmv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dabbbafd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E9%BB%8E%E6%9C%89%E5%88%80%E5%AE%A2%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%A6%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B74%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83-%E4%BC%8A%E6%96%AF%E8%98%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB-232357432.html</a>"},{"pid":"410d5fc9587923c652de9e9934c650e92dc083c0","tid":662981,"uid":60787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"左膠又添一筆血債"},{"pid":"09569c81a202920cf2468a2cbf3273c3e7f6d0e4","tid":662981,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi